<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Tele-Communications cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Tele-Communications cut.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- UBS Securities said in a research note it lowered its recommendation on Tele-Communications Inc to hold from buy.</p>
<p>-- &quot;We question the sustainability of current expense levels in light of the company's aggressive plans to upgrade its networks and roll out digital video (to) as much as 90 percent of its customer base by year-end. TCOMA shares are up 20 percent since April 21 and more than 30 percent from its low. We recommend that investors sell into strength, swapping TCOMA shares for Cox Communication Inc or U S West Media Group,&quot; the note said.</p>
<p>-- Tele-Communications shares were off 1/8 to 13-11/16 in morning Nasdaq trade.</p>
